make a cup of coffee

put water and coffee in the coffee maker and turn it on

make sure the coffee maker is empty;
if it isn't then -- empty the basket and any coffee in the beaker
if it is then, take the beaker to the sink and fill it with  N number of cups of water
return to the coffee maker and fill the resevoir with water;
get the coffee grounds out of the freezer;
fill the coffee filter cone with N+1 scoops of coffee;
close the lid and turn on the machine;
